        </div>
        <div class="nivoSlider" id="slider">
         <img alt="Honor Code Vision" class="slide" data-thumb="https://honorcode.byu.edu/sites/default/files/banner/maser_side.png" data-transition="" id="slide-0" src="https://honorcode.byu.edu/sites/default/files/banner/maser_side.png" title="#htmlcaption-0" typeof="foaf:Image"/>
         <img alt="The Wilk" class="slide" data-thumb="https://honorcode.byu.edu/sites/default/files/banner/HCBanner-Wilk.png" data-transition="" id="slide-1" src="https://honorcode.byu.edu/sites/default/files/banner/HCBanner-Wilk.png" title="" typeof="foaf:Image"/>
         <img alt="Maeser Statue" class="slide" data-thumb="https://honorcode.byu.edu/sites/default/files/banner/HCBanner-HonorQuote.png" data-transition="" id="slide-2" src="https://honorcode.byu.edu/sites/default/files/banner/HCBanner-HonorQuote.png" title="" typeof="foaf:Image"/>
         <img alt="Young Statue" class="slide" data-thumb="https://honorcode.byu.edu/sites/default/files/banner/HCBanner-YoungStatue2.png" data-transition="" id="slide-3" src="https://honorcode.byu.edu/sites/default/files/banner/HCBanner-YoungStatue2.png" title="" typeof="foaf:Image"/>
         <img alt="Maeser Memorial" class="slide" data-thumb="https://honorcode.byu.edu/sites/default/files/banner/memorial-pic.png" data-transition="" id="slide-4" src="https://honorcode.byu.edu/sites/default/files/banner/memorial-pic.png" title="" typeof="foaf:Image"/>
         <img alt="Devotional" class="slide" data-thumb="https://honorcode.byu.edu/sites/default/files/banner/HCBanner-Devotional2.png" data-transition="" id="slide-5" src="https://honorcode.byu.edu/sites/default/files/banner/HCBanner-Devotional2.png" title="" typeof="foaf:Image"/>
        </div>
       </div>
       <div class="nivo-html-caption" id="htmlcaption-0">
        <p>
         The vision of the Honor Code Office is   "To assist the BYU Community in their individual effort to emulate the Savior by honoring their commitment to the principles of the Honor Code."
        </p>
        <p>
         Part of our commitment is to support each other in living the principles outlined in the
         <a href="https://policy.byu.edu/view/index.php?p=26" target="_blank">
          Honor Code
         </a>
         .
        </p>
       </div>
      </div>
