           <div id="welcome-pane">
            <h2>
             Welcome
            </h2>
            <hr/>
            <p>
             If you are planning to register for fall semester 2019 you will need to complete a Continuing Student Ecclesiastical Endorsement. The online process is available on January 15, 2019. Go to
             <a href="https://endorse.byu.edu/" target="_blank">
              endorse.byu.edu
             </a>
             to begin the process.
            </p>
           </div>
           <p>
           </p>
